      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have to see this absolute gem to believe it! It\u2019s in truly spectacular shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for something that\u2019s been pampered and is ready to turn heads, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 46500.0,
