    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of Bavarian engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant with its signature individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically, this chassis is exceptional: the Vanos system has been fully serviced, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains tight, utilizing refreshed bushings and OEM dampers for factory-spec damping rates. With flawless paint depth and a cabin featuring immaculate Nappa leather, this is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the driver who values mechanical transparency and high-revving performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
