    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the wheels are free of any curb rash or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule. The premium leather upholstery remains supple with no visible bolster wear, and the original factory floor mats have been protected by deep-pile over-mats since new. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the ambient lighting, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has a comprehensive service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is detailed and dry, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a 'no-stories' vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
